mal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"著多件換裝都方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc57a5d9fd534569a47e3dbe8ff3cfd02f21872","tid":1679691,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=d4c42de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"f83fa164ebb747f1ee65e9c03880aa4f514ed059","tid":1679691,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6a7a66c0a049422feb6ee0d3d3fd7f810282ffa","tid":1679691,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"全民黑色褸"},{"pid":"6b1861f748c5d985721445c27dcc8f646835b7e9","tid":1679691,"uid":27814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔</span>：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』[1]"},{"pid":"a91076687a063c5b1f3adf14d6d24f98b999d9f9","tid":1679691,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83fa164ebb747f1ee65e9c03880aa4f514ed059","tid":1679691,"uid":235025,"like":1,"disli